{"type":"article","id":11721,"title":"向葱友们推荐一些画作，费拉化的中华民族","uid":1263,"topics":[1,681,163],"contents":"当我还是个政治冷感者的时候，我不能理解这些当代艺术家们的作品，觉得他们只是单纯丑化和讽刺政治，而且自我重复性过强。像是罗中立的《父亲》那种，才是油画该有的样子吧？但随着这么多年各种社会新闻的种种怪现状，我不得不佩服这些艺术家们的前瞻和犀利，请注意，以下作品基本上都是十几年前制作的，这些艺术家现今已呈隐退状态。至于有没有水平，大家可以自己判断。<br>\n岳敏君：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jyrBhxR.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jyrBhxR.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jyrBhxR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TtRuDsn.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TtRuDsn.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TtRuDsn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QixhfE0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QixhfE0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QixhfE0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZQUs4uF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZQUs4uF.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZQUs4uF.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fyBRfvT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fyBRfvT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fyBRfvT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z0uqpG3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z0uqpG3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z0uqpG3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n张晓刚<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/q8nauIG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q8nauIG.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/q8nauIG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JiDDn3H.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JiDDn3H.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.c